Aquatic Microbial Ecology bụ akwụkwọ akụkọ sayensị na-enyocha kwa ọnwa nke ndị ọgbọ na-ekpuchi akụkụ niile nke mgbanwe microbial mmiri, ọkachasị nje, prokaryotes na eukaryotes n'ime mmiri, limnetic, na ebe obibi brackish. P
Rassoulzadegan guzobere akwụkwọ akụkọ ahụ dị ka Marine Microbial Food Webs n'afọ 1985, wee nweta aha ya ugbu a n'afọ 1995. Ọ bụ Inter Research na-ebipụta akwụkwọ akụkọ ahụ ugbu a.
